{"tid":1426074,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"再見到藍絲撕連儂牆，可以試下咁","createTime":"2019-08-07T00:39:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-07T01:28:21.000Z","uid":126133,"like":32,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"0999ff158b577a03a93de068cc637b0ef19a061e","tid":1426074,"uid":126133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T00:39:30.000Z","msg":"拍片話佢係黃絲貼緊memo紙<br />\n佢實唔認㗎，再不斷話佢係暴徒破壞香港<br />\n等佢忍唔住出手<br />\n咁就可以send條片去港人講地嗰啲group<br />\n當然條片加啲剪接要拍到佢成個黃絲咁<br />\n嗰啲藍絲group一言堂跟本唔會獨立思考<br />\n見你出post就share<br />\n當佢地見到自己被屈被罵但又無人幫佢<br />\n又唔只撕紙喎，阻住車門嘅又可以話佢搞事喎<br />\n只要口才好，就可以子之矛坆子之盾!!"},{"pid":"918670b95181e43579d9f3b1fb512edaea02ca6a","tid":1426074,"uid":281135,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T00:40:44.000Z","msg":"我寧願打救佢算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4f6e9c5479545d17c6822d6d1a5d7b58708832b","tid":1426074,"uid":126133,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"918670b95181e43579d9f3b1fb512edaea02ca6a","tid":1426074,"uid":281135,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T00:40:44.000Z","msg":"我寧願打救佢算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T00:42:09.000Z","msg":"咁咪得你打佢條片囉，又話你係暴徒喇"},{"pid":"12953a1d44f9aa4ec859ca7476be84c122c199a9","tid":1426074,"uid":36588,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T00:43:06.000Z","msg":"叫埋佢一齊貼"},{"pid":"74a9c7c76ff4540a2d179324d388cdad4d7dd9ca","tid":1426074,"uid":22288,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T00:43:35.000Z"